Download VIM
http://www.vim.org/download.php

Download GIT (allow call from cmd)
http://git-scm.com/downloads

Copy curl to C:\Program Files\Git\cmd\

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
WINDOWS
Installation:
	git clone git://github.com/brodroll/dotvim.git %userprofile%\vimfiles

Create symlinks:
	mklink %userprofile%\_vimrc %userprofile%\vimfiles\_vimrc

UNIX
Installation:
	git clone git://github.com/brodroll/dotvim.git ~/vimfiles

Create symlinks:
	ln -s ~/vimfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/vimfiles/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Install VUNDLE in the vimfiles/bundle folder (simply clone repository):
https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim

WINDOWS
git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git %userprofile%/vimfiles/bundle/Vundle.vim

UNIX
git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git ~/vimfiles/bundle/Vundle.vim

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Open vim and type: :PluginInstall or :PluginUpdate

